Use the standard library
This is how to do_algebra of operator and operand:
   Remember that result is item 0 in operand
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this operator's length times:
      Remember that op is item i in operator
      Remember that value is item (sum of i and 1) in operand
      When op is "+", then:
         Remember that result is sum of result and value
      But, if not:
         When op is "-", then:
            Remember that result is diff of result and value
         But, if not:
            When op is "*", then:
               Remember that result is product of result and value
            But, if not:
               When op is "**", then:
                  Remember that power is 1
                  Remember that j is 0
                  Do this value times:
                     Remember that power is product of power and result
                     Increase j
                  End do
                  Remember that result is power
               End when
            End when
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is result
Now you know